  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The current contract has the following function:\r\n\r\n```\r\n  function finishMinting()\r\n    public\r\n    onlyMinter\r\n    onlyBeforeMintingFinished\r\n    returns (bool)\r\n  {\r\n    _mintingFinished = true;\r\n    emit MintingFinished();\r\n    return true;\r\n  }\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis, in effect, is equivalent to giving all minters permission to remove all other minters (and themselves) from the minter group, which goes against the minimal assumption model we've been following for the Roles feature: we should get rid of it.",
